OL,7,FA retired teacher has been told she is
OL,8,Fnot eligible for a specially adapted
OL,9,Fcar to help her get around because she
OL,10,Fis of "pensionable age".
OL,12,FSue Allcock says her life changed
OL,13,Fovernight when she suddenly lost
OL,14,Ffeeling in both her legs, due spinal
OL,15,Fcord compression, in November 2023.
OL,17,FThe usually busy 74-year-old, from
OL,18,FGlossop, regularly took care of her
OL,19,Fgrandchildren, travellws in her
OL,20,Fmotorhome, and is a big part of her
OL,21,Flocal cricket club.
