OL,7,FBut she can no longer stand on her own
OL,8,Fand now needs a wheelchair to get
OL,9,Faround.
OL,11,FAfter applying for help to fund a
OL,12,Fspecial motability vehicle to keep her
OL,13,Findependence, she was told she did not
OL,14,Fqualify, and was too old.
OL,16,FSue has now had to use a large part of
OL,17,Fher #22,000 savings to buy an ex-
OL,18,Fmotability van to ensure she is able
OL,19,Fto get around.
