OL,7,FShe has also had to move her bed to
OL,8,Fher living room and pay #600 a week
OL,9,Ffor carers to get her out of bed in
OL,10,Fthe morning, washed and dressed before
OL,11,Fhelping her back to bed at night.
OL,13,F"My life has just totally changed from
OL,14,Fupstairs to downstairs and I need help
OL,15,Fto do everyday things".
OL,17,FJo Williams, Sue's daughter and a
OL,18,Fphysiotherapist, is moving her family
OL,19,Fcloser to her mum to be able to help
OL,20,Falong with her brother.
