OL,7,FBut the family were shocked to find
OL,8,Fout Sue is not eligible for a
OL,9,Fmotability vehicle because of her age.
OL,11,FJo said: "I'm angry if I'm honest, my
OL,12,Fmum doesn't have anything left from
OL,13,Fpaying for her carers, which is more
OL,14,Fthan the Attendance Allowance she
OL,15,Freceives, and there is nothing left to
OL,16,Fhelp with her mobility."
