OL,8,Fthe spinal condition before she was
OL,9,F65, and had received her state
OL,10,Fpension, she would have been able to
OL,11,Fget an adapted vehicle as part of a
OL,12,Fbenefits package.
OL,14,FBut instead, as the former the
OL,15,Fteacher, who has worked all her life,
OL,16,Fhas drawn her pension, and is above
OL,17,F65, she does not qualify.
