OL,7,Fwho survived the Manchester Arena bomb
OL,8,Fattack and is a disability advocate,
OL,9,Fmet Sue while filming a special series
OL,10,Ffor ITV Granada Reports highlighting
OL,11,Fthe challenges disabled people face
OL,12,Fevery day.
OL,14,F"It is shocking that in 2024 that
OL,15,Fdisabled people are treated like
OL,16,Fsecond class citizens, and that's what
